trans-unit.source: Consists of a collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects to be used with catalogs of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"></xref> controls.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> 개체를 카탈로그와 함께 사용할 수 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart"> </xref> 컨트롤입니다.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: 이 클래스는 상속 될 수 없습니다.

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is created by the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls in their implementations of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method.
trans-unit.target: 여러 WebPartDescriptionCollection 클래스를 만들 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>컨트롤의 구현에서는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>메서드.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: For each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control that is contained in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control, a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object is created.
trans-unit.target: 각각에 대해 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>컨트롤에 포함 된 한 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>컨트롤은 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>개체가 만들어집니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: This object maintains basic information about a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control, including its ID, its title, its description, and a path to an associated icon.
trans-unit.target: 이 개체에 대 한 기본 정보를 유지 관리는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>ID, 제목, 설명 및 연결 된 아이콘에 대 한 경로 포함 하 여 제어 합니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>

trans-unit.source: The various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls can use a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to display a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control's information in the catalog, without having to create an instance of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control itself.
trans-unit.target: 다양 한 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>컨트롤 צ ְ ײ는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>표시할 개체는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>의 인스턴스를 만들 필요 없이 카탈로그에서 컨트롤의 정보는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>컨트롤 자체.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection class is used internally by the Web Parts control set to maintain a collection of all the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects used in a catalog.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDescriptionCollection 클래스의 모든 컬렉션을 유지 하기 위해 설정 하는 웹 파트 컨트롤에서 내부적으로 사용 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>카탈로그에 사용 되는 개체입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection collection is used only when a page is in catalog display mode.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDescriptionCollection 컬렉션 페이지 카탈로그 디스플레이 모드에 있을 경우에 사용 됩니다.

trans-unit.source: When a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> control is being rendered, it loops through the WebPartDescriptionCollection collection, adding the information from each <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> object to the displayed catalog.
trans-unit.target: 경우는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>컨트롤 렌더링 되 고, 각에서 정보를 추가 WebPartDescriptionCollection 컬렉션을 반복 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>개체 표시 된 카탈로그입니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>

trans-unit.source: Initializes an empty new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: 비어 있는 새 인스턴스를 초기화는 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> 클래스입니다.

trans-unit.source: This overload of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A> constructor can be used to create an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: 이 오버 로드는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>생성자는 빈 컬렉션을 만드는 데 사용할 수 있습니다.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection.%23ctor%2A>

trans-unit.source: For example, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.ImportCatalogPart> control creates an empty <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection> object if the content of an imported description file is `null`.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of a <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"></xref> object by passing in an <xref:System.Collections.ICollection> collection of <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"></xref> objects.
trans-unit.target: 새 인스턴스를 초기화 한 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescriptionCollection"> </xref> 전달 하 여 개체는 <xref:System.Collections.ICollection>의 컬렉션 <xref href="System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription"> </xref> 개체.</xref:System.Collections.ICollection>

trans-unit.source: The WebPartDescriptionCollection constructor is used by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A> method implementations within the various <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> controls to create a collection of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> objects.
trans-unit.target: WebPartDescriptionCollection 생성자가 사용 되는 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>내의 다양 한 메서드 구현 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart>컨트롤의 컬렉션을 만들려면 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription>개체.</xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartDescription> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart> </xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.CatalogPart.GetAvailableWebPartDescriptions%2A>
